creator: Dizzy Gillespie y Arturo Sandoval
description:
Dizzy Gillespie traveled to Cuba in May of 1977 on a jazz tour of the Caribbean. It was then that he and other jazz greats met Arturo Sandoval. Gillespie became Sandoval’s mentor and close friend.

Buy Arturo Sandoval's music at J.W. Pepper: https://www.jwpepper.com/sheet-music/search.jsp?redirect=2017-arturo-sandoval-music&pageview=grid-view&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=jazz-100&utm_content=sandoval-video7
